### [CRIT-02] Missing Content-Security-Policy (CSP) Header

**File:** `next.config.ts`  
**Severity:** HIGH  
**Kategori:** OWASP A05 - Security Misconfiguration

**Masalah:** File `next.config.ts` sudah bagus — ada `X-Frame-Options`, `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Referrer-Policy`. **Namun tidak ada `Content-Security-Policy`**. Tanpa CSP, jika ada celah XSS yang ditemukan di masa depan (misal dari library third-party), browser tidak punya lapisan pertahanan untuk mencegah eksekusi script berbahaya.

Klinik menangani data sensitif (NIK, No HP) — CSP adalah wajib.

**Rekomendasi:** Tambahkan CSP ke `next.config.ts`:

```typescript
// next.config.ts
const securityHeaders = [
  { key: "X-Content-Type-Options", value: "nosniff" },
  { key: "X-Frame-Options", value: "DENY" },
  { key: "Referrer-Policy", value: "strict-origin-when-cross-origin" },
  { key: "Permissions-Policy", value: "camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()" },
  {
    key: "Content-Security-Policy",
    value: [
      "default-src 'self'",
      "script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'",  // 'unsafe-inline' diperlukan Framer Motion
      "style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com",
      "font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com",
      "img-src 'self' data: https://images.unsplash.com https://*.supabase.co",
      "connect-src 'self' https://*.supabase.co",
      "frame-src https://www.google.com",  // untuk Google Maps embed
    ].join("; "),
  },
  {
    key: "Strict-Transport-Security",
    value: "max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload",
  },
];
```

