## 🟡 Temuan Medium (Perlu Diperbaiki Sebelum atau Sesaat Setelah Go-Live)

### [MED-01] Supabase Client Diinisialisasi di `lib/supabase.ts` Bisa Crash di Build Time

**File:** `lib/supabase.ts`  
**Severity:** MEDIUM  
**Kategori:** Runtime Error

**Masalah:**
```typescript
if (!supabaseUrl || !supabaseAnonKey) {
  throw new Error('Missing Supabase environment variables');
}
```

`throw` di module-level menyebabkan **build Next.js gagal total** jika variabel env tidak ada (misal saat CI/CD pipeline belum dikonfigurasi). Lebih baik gunakan lazy initialization.

**Rekomendasi:**
```typescript
// lib/supabase.ts
import { createClient, SupabaseClient } from '@supabase/supabase-js';

let _supabase: SupabaseClient | null = null;

export const getSupabase = () => {
  if (_supabase) return _supabase;
  const url = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL;
  const key = process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY;
  if (!url || !key) throw new Error('[Supabase] Missing env vars. Check .env.local');
  _supabase = createClient(url, key);
  return _supabase;
};

// Backward compat (opsional):
export const supabase = typeof window !== 'undefined' ? getSupabase() : null as any;
```

